# Czech Quiz Application - Project Overview

This is a comprehensive web-based quiz application written in Czech language called "Kvízový Mistr" (Quiz Master). The application allows users to create, manage, and play interactive quizzes with multimedia support.

## Main Entry Points

- **[index.html](mdc:index.html)** - Main quiz application interface with landing screen, quiz setup, and gameplay
- **[quiz.js](mdc:quiz.js)** - Core quiz logic, state management, and gameplay functionality (42KB)
- **[config-loader.js](mdc:config-loader.js)** - Configuration system with embedded settings for customization

## Builder Tools

The application includes several builder tools for content creation:

- **[topic-builder.html](mdc:topic-builder.html)** + **[topic-builder.js](mdc:topic-builder.js)** - Tool for creating quiz topics with questions
- **[quiz-builder.html](mdc:quiz-builder.html)** + **[quiz-builder.js](mdc:quiz-builder.js)** - Tool for combining topics into complete quizzes
- **[prompt-generator.html](mdc:prompt-generator.html)** + **[prompt-generator.js](mdc:prompt-generator.js)** - AI prompt generator for quiz content
- **[theme-designer.html](mdc:theme-designer.html)** + **[theme-designer.js](mdc:theme-designer.js)** - Visual theme customization tool

## Styling and Themes

- **[styles.css](mdc:styles.css)** - Main application styles (29KB, 1536 lines)
- **[theme.css](mdc:theme.css)** - Base theme definitions
- **[themes/](mdc:themes)** directory contains pre-built themes like `ocean-blue.css`, `default-dark.css`
- Each builder tool has its own dedicated CSS file

## Content Structure

- **[topics/](mdc:topics)** - JSON files containing quiz questions organized by topic
- **[quizzes/](mdc:quizzes)** - Complete quiz configurations combining multiple topics
- **[images/](mdc:images)** and **[audio/](mdc:audio)** - Media assets for questions
- **[timer.js](mdc:timer.js)** - Standalone timer functionality

## Key Features

- Multi-topic quiz system with configurable rounds
- Multimedia support (images, audio)
- Customizable themes and branding
- Timer-based questions
- Progress tracking and scoring
- Responsive design
- Works offline (no server required)
- Configurable UI text and messages through embedded configuration

